<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic styling for the email */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Order Confirmation</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= order.user %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for your order of the " <%= order.name%>" course.</p>
        <p>**Order Summary:**</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Course Name: <%= order.name%></li>
            <li>Price: <%= order.price%></li>
            <li>Order ID: <%= order._id%></li>
            <li>Order Date: <%= order.date%></li>
        </ul>
        <p>You will receive an email with login credentials and course access instructions shortly.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at [Support Email].</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        Best regards,<br>
        The [LMS Name] Team
    </div>
</body>
</html>